text: Kieren Paley (born 3 October 1990) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites == * Kieran+Paley zimbio Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
